column6: Nice quite Neighborhood, one room with full size bed, a crib for the baby or toddler, also have a air mattress available if needed. Restroom is right next door to room also there is a game area, and large back yard. Parking in drive way. Stove and refrigerator down stairs if needed. Close to George Bush Airport. Walmart and Kroger and HEB & Starbucks close by.
column9: Comfortable family room w/ full bed
